    "layoutDecisions": "The layout follows a single-column vertical list, mirroring the reference image's structure for intuitive navigation.  Sections are grouped logically for better user understanding. Item spacing is minimized to maximize screen real estate, while maintaining adequate visual breathing room between sections.  The screen-level auto-layout ensures that all navigation elements touch screen edges, maintaining visual consistency with the app's design system.",
